TITLE

* Set the defaults for precision simulations
DEFAULTS                                                              HADROTHE
BEAM            -0.1     0.001                  1.        1.          PROTON
BEAMPOS                              -5.
SOURCE         -205.                                                  sobp.dat
GEOBEGIN                                                              COMBNAME
    0    0          
* Black body
SPH blkbody    0.0 0.0 0.0 100000.
* Void sphere
SPH void       0.0 0.0 0.0 10000.
RPP target     -30. 30. -30. 30. 0.0 21.
END
* Black hole
BLKBODY      5 +blkbody -void
* Void around
VOID         5 +void -target
* Target
TARGET       5 +target
END
GEOEND
* ..+....1....+....2....+....3....+....4....+....5....+....6....+....7..
ASSIGNMA    BLCKHOLE   BLKBODY
ASSIGNMA      VACUUM      VOID
ASSIGNMA       WATER    TARGET
USRBIN           10.      DOSE      -21.       20.       10.       12.XY_dose
USRBIN          -20.      -10.        1.      600.      600.        1. &
USRBIN           10.      DOSE      -22.       20.       10.       12.XZ_dose
USRBIN          -20.      -10.        1.      600.        1.      200. &
USRBIN           10.      DOSE      -23.       20.       10.       12.YZ_dose
USRBIN          -20.      -10.        1.        1.      600.      200. &
USRBIN           10.      DOSE      -24.       20.       10.       12.Z_dose
USRBIN          -20.      -10.        1.        1.        1.      200. &
* Set the random number seed
RANDOMIZ          1.
* Set the number of primary histories to be simulated in the run
START         20000.
STOP
